Custom Settings for Vim
=======================

INSTALL
-------

* cd ~

* git clone git@github.com:olarcheveque/vim.git ~/.vim

* ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc .vimrc

* cd ~/.vim

* ./up_submodule.sh


MODULES
-------

* nerdtree  : https://github.com/vim-scripts/The-NERD-tree.git

* pep8      : https://github.com/vim-scripts/pep8.git

* pyflakes  : https://github.com/mitechie/pyflakes-pathogen.git

* snipmate  : https://github.com/msanders/snipmate.vim.git

* vim-align : https://github.com/tsaleh/vim-align.git


CUSTOM
------

<F5> : PEP8

<F9> : NerdTree

AUTO : PyFlakes

<SELECTION>Align<CHAR><CR> : align on the char

:call TrimSpaces() : trim spaces
